{"type":null,"faqId":38465,"title":"录制视频","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p4{margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:12pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125267\" style=\"width:0.24305555in;height:0.1875in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“相机”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>左右滑动屏幕，选择“录像”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125268\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，开始录制视频。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>录制过程中，点击不同对象或区域可进行对焦，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125269\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”可暂停录制，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125270\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”可继续录制。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125271\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，结束录制。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125272\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>在录制过程中，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125273\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”可将当前镜头存为照片。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":3,"unUseful":6,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3745","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441442755000,"seriesProductName":"GRA-CL00,GRA-CL10,GRA-TL00,GRA-UL00,GRA-UL10","visitedTimes":48,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"录制视频","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}